---
title: Plantain and Black Bean Tostadas with Pickled Red Onion, Avocado and Feta
description: Plantains are a staple of Latin and South American cuisine. Tonight, we're frying them into maduros - the star of these tostadas. Paired with pickled onion, the creaminess of avocado, and smoky cumin, each bite has the perfect balance of flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/plantain-and-black-bean-tostadas-a18f883f.jpg
